    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several deep scratches, noticeable dents, and areas of rust. Mechanically, the car is currently running but needs immediate repairs to the suspension and likely an engine overhaul to be reliable. The interior has sustained considerable damage over the years, with visible tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is a project car or a parts vehicle for someone prepared to invest the necessary time and resources into a full restoration.",
      "price": 6500.0,
